r than Third Point=E2=80=99s.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is always a chicken-and-egg quality to t=
hese things: Neumann obviously can=E2=80=99t line up committed financing to=
 buy WeWork without getting due diligence information and some engagement f=
